*<br> <br></span>Whether through the path of wisdom or surrender, deve=
lop dispassion and detachment. Realize that all this is temporary and can b=
e taken away anytime. Enjoy it while you have and keep doing your best, but=
 be prepared to lose everything anytime. Only detachment and a very light m=
ental conditioning (very light desires, dislikes etc) can protect one as on=
e's Kundalini rises to meet True Self. Heavy conditioning and impurities in=
 one's nadis will distract rising Kundalini (self-awareness) and stop Her f=
